==Een haven bouwen==

'''1.''' Open de ''Waterwegen constructies'' knoppenbalk door te klikken op de [[File:en/Manual/Manual html m2cc0c4cd.png]] knop.
[[File:en/Manual/Dock toolbar.png|frame|none|De waterwegen constructie knoppenbalk]]

'''2.''' Klik op de ''Bouw haven'' knop [[File:en/Manual/Build dock.png]]. Een ''Haven bouwvenster'' wordt getoond. Denk eraan, je kunt rechtsklikken op elke knop als je een beschrijving wilt van wat deze knop doet.

'''3.''' Move the mouse along the edge of the water: the dock needs to be placed on a sloped tile that is connected to a water tile.

'''4.''' Keep an eye on the ''Dock building window'' and make sure that ''Oil'' is displayed after ''Accepts'' before building the dock.

'''5.''' If the cursor displayes two white squares '''and''' oil is accepted at the location you picked, just click with the left mouse button to place the dock (possibly you'll have to [[en/Manual/Landscaping|terraform]] a bit first in order to create a suitable location).
[[File:en/Manual/Dock construction 2.png|frame|none|After some [[en/Manual/Landscaping|terraforming]], we've found a suitable location for our dock. Note the acceptance of Oil in the Waterways construction window.]]


[[File:en/Manual/Dock construction 3.png|frame|right|Our newly constructed dock.]]
And that's all there is to building a dock! In order to buy a ship to transport the oil, you'll have to construct a ship depot first.

